  $ export PYTHONPATH

Check diagnosis, debugging information
1) Setup configuration
  $ mkcommit() {
  >    echo "$1" > "$1"
  >    hg add "$1"
  >    echo "add $1" > msg
  >    echo "" >> msg
  >    hg ci -l msg
  > }

2) Create a repo with a bunch of revs.

  $ mkdir concurrency
  $ cd concurrency
  $ hg init
  $ cat >> .hg/hgrc << EOF
  > [extensions]
  > fastmanifest=$TESTDIR/../fastmanifest
  > [fastmanifest]
  > cachecutoffdays=-1
  > cacheonchange=True
  > cacheonchangebackground=True
  > EOF
  $ mkcommit a
  $ mkcommit b
  $ mkcommit c
  $ mkcommit d
  $ mkcommit e
this is a barrier to ensure that any cache workers that we've kicked off
